      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-05-12T14:19:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I remember we talked about having a fSubmittedProc(void* flushContext) in GrFlushInfo, it can be used to indicate if a flush is submitted to GPU successfully. Will it work?",
      "parentUuid": "3a2f79d6_30138902",
